{
  "stem": "13911.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Work in the field.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were not allowed to walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were supposed to run with the bundles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never found out exactly, in English, what you call them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because in Ukraine, you see these bundles of wheat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You tied them in the field when it's done, when it's harvested.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'll still have to find-- certain things I have to find out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we had to do-- work-- all under the machine that was grinding the-- the wheat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was a German and a horse, swift horse, with a long whip.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And whipping.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Whipping left and right, so you were just running and trying to escape him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I even got a slap on my face.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean now, I could never tolerate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, maybe I would if-- no, I'm not in the position to say anything-- but I would just die right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then anything they-- they did to you, it was, what else do you expect?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He thought that I'm putting too much of those bundles in the machine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were feeding on top of the machine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He thought-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would never do anything that I'm not supposed to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this is what he thought, the German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he gave me a slap up on my cheek, like stars were flying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's a terrible feeling, you know, when you get-- but anyway, you did not feel very important anyway, like you amounted to nothing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think-- I don't think you were even could afford such a luxury.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, crying, laughing, hey, these are luxuries.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You were just a number to be slaughtered soon.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
